# Full Markdown Support

Polyester now supports **GitHub Flavored Markdown** including:

## Text Formatting

- **Bold text** and *italic text*
- ~~Strikethrough~~ text
- `Inline code` snippets
- [Links](https://example.com)

## Lists

1. First item
2. Second item
   - Nested bullet
   - Another nested item
3. Third item

## Code Blocks

```javascript
function greet(name) {
  console.log(`Hello, ${name}!`);
}
```

